# Allowlisting gitignore template for GO projects prevents us
# from adding various unwanted local files, such as generated
# files, developer configurations or IDE-specific files etc.
#
# Recommended: Go.AllowList.gitignore

# Ignore everything
*

# But not these files...
!/.gitattributes
!/.gitignore
!/.dockerignore
!.github/**

!scripts/*

!config-example.yaml
!Dockerfile
!docker-compose.yml

!*.go
!go.sum
!go.mod
!*.html

!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENSE

# Fuzz corpus files have no extension, so allowlist them explicitly
!internal/media/testdata/fuzz/**

# ...even if they are in subdirectories
!*/

# Hard blocks
tmp/
bin/
